erties to be well reproduced in\nthis approach. However, as many have concluded before us, we find that pairing\ncorrelations are unlikely to provide an answer to the question of ''why is Tin\nso soft?''\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2013 00:41:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
